Experiment 8: Compare Documents & Secure a Word File

Compare Two Word Documents:

1. Open one version of your document in Word.


2. Go to Review > Compare > Compareâ€¦.


3. In the dialogue, choose the Original document and then browse to select the Revised document.


4. Click OK. Word will highlight changes between the two documents.



Set Document Security (Password Protect):

1. Open your document.


2. Go to File > Info > Protect Document > Encrypt with Password.


3. Enter a password (e.g., MySecurePass123) and click OK.


4. Save the document.
